                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "…Exploding pasta?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_0_0_tb_4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "It's been an intense day."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_0_0_tb_5",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow nods slowly. The kind of nod that doesn't mean yes at all."
                }
              ],
              "interactions": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 1,
          "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_ritorno_casa/ivb_1.webp",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "ivbi_1_0",
              "characters": [
                "lex",
                "favilla"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_1_0_tb_0",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex sees Favilla. TAPPATAP TAPPATAP on the floor. Then turns to Mallow with a solemn look."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_1_0_tb_1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "He's been doing that all day. I think he's learning to communicate."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_1_0_tb_2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex: face saying \"you're getting there\"."
                }
              ],
              "interactions": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 2,
          "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_ritorno_casa/ivb_2.webp",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "ivbi_2_0",
              "characters": [
                "lex",
                "favilla",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_2_0_tb_0",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "ATTEMPT 1: Lex crawls toward Favilla. With surgical precision, he grabs the hem of the burned blouse with both little hands. Pulls. Pulls toward Mallow."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_2_0_tb_1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "BAAAAAAAH!!"
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_2_0_tb_2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Favilla catches it in a millisecond. Mallow turns around."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_2_0_tb_3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "What's wrong?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_2_0_tb_4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "He wants to play. He always wants to be picked up."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_2_0_tb_5",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex: face saying \"that's a lie and we both know it\"."
                }
              ],
              "interactions": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 3,
          "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_ritorno_casa/ivb_3.webp",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "ivbi_3_0",
              "characters": [
                "lex",
                "favilla",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_3_0_tb_0",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "ATTEMPT 2: Lex takes Favilla's hand. Points it at the blouse. At the scorch mark. With the precision of a six-kilo detective."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_3_0_tb_1",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Mallow isn't looking. He's chopping an onion with the dedication of a man who heard absolutely nothing."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_3_0_tb_2",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Fingers. He likes fingers. It's a phase."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_3_0_tb_3",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex lets go of the finger. Snorts. That was humiliating."
                }
              ],
              "interactions": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "index": 4,
          "background": "assets/episodes/s1/s1_ritorno_casa/ivb_4.webp",
          "panels": [
            {
              "id": "ivbi_4_0",
              "characters": [
                "lex",
                "favilla",
                "mallow"
              ],
              "text_blocks": [
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_0",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "FINAL ATTEMPT: Lex snaps both arms up — WHOOSH — drops them. Raises them. Drops them. Three times, with growing emphasis. Then he points his tiny finger at Favilla and makes his explosion face — cheeks puffed, blowing out all his air."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_1",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "He wants to fly too. Like mummy."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_2",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Silence."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_3",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "...Just like mummy?"
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_4",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "mallow",
                  "text": "Well. You always seem to be rushing lately. Like you're flying."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_5",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "A very long pause."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_6",
                  "type": "dialogue",
                  "speaker": "favilla",
                  "text": "Yes. I'm just tired."
                },
                {
                  "id": "ivbi_4_0_tb_7",
                  "type": "narration",
                  "text": "Lex stares at her. He did his best."
                }
              ],
              "interactions": []
            }
          ],
